Creating timedelta objects

 the timedelta object only stores days, seconds, and microseconds internally. 

from datetime import timedelta

delta = timedelta(weeks=2, days=2, hours=3)
print(delta)
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
